✔︎ ghouls in labradorite and obsidian 
✔︎ pumpkins 🎃 in orange jade, white jade, and yooperlite (super fun 🤩 fluorescing sodalite)
✔︎ bats 🦇 in yooperlite, obsidian, and selenite
✔︎ snakes in labradorite and selenite 
✔︎ BRAINS 🧠!!! Yes, brains how fun! They have clear quartz, rose quartz, and fire quartz

✔︎ and so much more!
